<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="Aink203-kilavi"> uṭaṉpōy mīṇṭa talaimakaḷ nī ceṉṟa nāṭṭu nīr iṉiyavalla nī eṅṅaṉam nukarntā yeṉak kēṭṭa tōḻikkuk kūṟiyatu.</p>

      <p xml:lang="en"> What the heroine who went together and returned, told the friend who asked “The waters from the land you went to are not sweet. How did you drink [them]?” </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink203 ">
<l>aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉainam paṭappait</l>
<l>tēṉmayaṅku pāliṉu miṉiya vavarnāṭ</l>
<l>ṭuvalaik kūvaṟ kīḻa</l>
<l>māṉuṇ ṭeñciya kaliḻi  nīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh Mother, please Mother, </l>
          <l rend="space indent"> sweeter than milk mixed with honey from our garden </l>
          <l rend="indent">were the muddy waters left behind after the deer drank</l>
          <l rend="indent">from the bottom of the well, [covered] with dried leaves. </l>
          
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
